vote.title: Authorize a twenty-four-month annual funding agreement with the Dallas Arboretum and Botanical Society, Inc. to provide services and program support within the City of Dallas in the amount of $424,393.00 for the period of January 1, 2024, through December 31, 2024; and in the amount of $424,393.00 for the period of January 1, 2025, through December 31, 2025 - Not to exceed $848,786.00 - Financing: General Fund
